---
// Footer component for Minecraft server
---

<footer class="bg-slate-950 border-t-2 border-green-500/20 py-12">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
    <!-- Main footer content -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-8">
      <!-- Logo & Description -->
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <img src="/logo.png" width="40" alt="NewJeans Logo" />
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white">NEWJEANS</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-md">
          Bienvenido a NewJeans, el servidor de Minecraft de Sword PvP. Únete a
          nuestra comunidad y disfruta de una experiencia única en el mundo de
          Minecraft. Conéctate, compite y diviértete con jugadores de todo el
          mundo. ¡Te esperamos en NewJeans!
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick Links -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-green-400 font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider">
          Quick Links
        </h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li>
            <a
              href="/"
              class="text-gray-400 hover:text-green-400 transition-colors"
              >Home</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="/rules"
              class="text-gray-400 hover:text-green-400 transition-colors"
              >Rules</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="/tierlist"
              class="text-gray-400 hover:text-green-400 transition-colors"
              >Tierlist</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="/forums"
              class="text-gray-400 hover:text-green-400 transition-colors"
              >Forums</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Connect -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-green-400 font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider">
          Connect
        </h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li>
            <a
              href="/"
              class="text-gray-400 hover:text-green-400 transition-colors"
              >Discord</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="/"
              class="text-gray-400 hover:text-green-400 transition-colors"
              >Store</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="/"
              class="text-gray-400 hover:text-green-400 transition-colors"
              >Vote</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="mailto:support@newjeans.net"
              class="text-gray-400 hover:text-green-400 transition-colors"
              >Support</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Copyright -->
    <div
      class="pt-8 border-t border-green-500/10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4"
    >
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">
        © {new Date().getFullYear()} NewJeans Minecraft Server. Not affiliated with
        Mojang or Microsoft.
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-sm text-gray-500">
        <span
          >Made with ❤️ for <a
            href="https://github.com/rodriguezemir"
            class="hover:text-gray-400"
            target="_blank">volcqnn</a
          ></span
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
